io.orchestrate.client.dao
Interface AsyncDao<T>

Type Parameters:
T - The type this object will control CRUD operations for.
All Known Implementing Classes:
GenericAsyncDao
public interface AsyncDao<T>

Interface for generic Create, Read, Update, and Delete (CRUD) operations on a collection for the specified type.
